ALRIGHT, AT THE FIDDLER ON THE ROOF I SAW MY FRIEND JACKIE. WE'RE AT THE PLACE AND I'M JUST THERE FOR EXTRA CREDIT, LIKE U'LL EVERY SEE ME THERE JUST 2 WATCH PPL. WELL IM THERE AND THIS GIRL IS SITTIN NEXT 2 ME NAMED JESSICA AND JACKIE KNEW HER AND THE SHOW WAS 4 HOURS LONG, YES 4 FREAKIN HOURS. WUT WOULDA GUY DO JUST 4 EXTRA CREDIT. BLAH BLAH BLAH 4GET THAT NIGHT. NOW IT'S THE NEXT DAY AND I HAD TO COME 2 SKOOL CUZ OF BAND. SO MR. BIMM COMES OUT OF NO WHERE. AND SAYS "MOISE COME TO MY OFFICE!" I WAS WONDERIN WUT THE HELL DID I DO NOW. SO THIS IS HOW THE CONVO. WENT.

ME- YES MR BIMM
MR. BIMM- WERE U AT THE FIDDLER ON THE ROOF YESTERDAY?
ME- YES I WAS
MR. BIMM- NOW WHO WAS W/ U?

SO I TOLD HIM THE TRUTH CUZ I KNOW JACKIE DIDNT DO ANYTHIN NOR THE OTHER PPL AROUND ME, BUT THAT'S WUT I THOUGHT

MR. BIMM- WELL, DID U C A BLONDE WOMAN SITTING NEAR THE BACK WEARING BLACK. POSSIBLY 4 ROWS IN FRONT OF THE BACK ROW.
ME- UM, I COULD OF IF I USE MY IMAGINATION
MR. BIMM- WELL 3 YOUNG MEN WERE BEING DISRUPTIVE AND SHE TOLD THEM 2 BE QUIET AND THEY RESPONDED BY SAYING "SHUT UP UR NOT A TEACHER HERE. U DONT TELL US WUT TO DO."

I'M LIKE WTF LITERALLY WUT THE FREAKIDY freak HOW DID I GET INTO THIS? SO MR. BIMM TOLD ME TO FIND THE KIDS WHO DID IT WEN I'M NOT EVEN SURE THEY GO TO MY SKOOL. YEA I KNO MESSED UP.
